Header include order:
 - Alphabetize within subgroups, newlines between groups
 - System group
   - linux/*
   - sys/types.h
   - sys/*
   - networking
 - C group
   - headers directly in /usr/include (e.g. fcntl.h, unistd.h)
 - C++ group
   - Standard C++ headers
   - TR1 headers (e.g. tr1/memory)
   - Boost headers
 - Library groups
   - external libraries (e.g. OpenSSL), grouped by library
